name: DREAM Unlimited Corp. Class A Subordinate Voting Shares
longDescription: DREAM Unlimited Corp is a real estate company. The company's divisions include Asset management; Stabilized income generating assets; Urban development - Toronto and Ottawa and Western Canada community development. It generates maximum revenue from the Asset Management segment. Its segments are Recurring income and Development.
